---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="The Breakthrough - Greenfield Platform"
  description="How bounded contexts unlock AI's full potential to build production-ready software without hallucinations or errors."
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-black text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-orange-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            The Breakthrough
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-100 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            How we finally unlocked AI's ability to build complete, production-ready systems
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- The Problem Section -->
        <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-cyan-400">The Fundamental Problem</h2>
          <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-8 mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-orange-400">AI Can't Handle Real Software</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-100 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Current AI fails with production codebases. It hallucinates functions, loses track of architecture,
              and generates broken code. The larger the context, the worse it gets. AI's promise remains locked
              behind its inability to maintain coherence in complex systems.
            </p>
            <ul class="text-gray-100 space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange-400 mr-3">•</span>
                <span>AI hallucinates functions that don't exist</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange-400 mr-3">•</span>
                <span>Loses track of system architecture</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange-400 mr-3">•</span>
                <span>Creates bugs faster than they can be fixed</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange-400 mr-3">•</span>
                <span>Can't be trusted with production systems</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="text-orange-400 mr-3">•</span>
                <span>The more it tries to do, the worse it performs</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- The Solution Section -->
        <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-cyan-400">The Universal Solution</h2>
          <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-8 mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-cyan-400">Perfect AI Boundaries</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-100 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
              The breakthrough: architect software so AI never loses context. Bounded contexts give AI perfect understanding
              of each piece. No hallucinations. No confusion. Just AI that builds production-ready code with 100% accuracy.
            </p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-cyan-400">Zero Hallucinations</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-100">
                  AI never loses track. Every context is complete and isolated. Perfect accuracy every time.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-orange-400">AI Builds Everything</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-100">
                  From MVPs to enterprise systems. AI handles any scale when given proper boundaries.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-cyan-400">100x Faster Development</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-100">
                  AI builds complete features in minutes, not weeks. Ship daily, not quarterly.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-orange-400">Production-Ready Output</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-100">
                  AI output you can deploy immediately. No debugging, no fixes, just working code.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Why It Works Section -->
        <section class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-cyan-400">Why This Works for Everything</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-cyan-400">Any Project Size</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-100">
                From solo projects to enterprise systems with millions of users. Bounded contexts scale infinitely
                because they divide complexity instead of adding to it.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-orange-400">Any Project Age</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-100">
                Brand new greenfield projects and 15-year legacy monoliths. The approach works by creating new
                bounded contexts that gradually absorb complexity from existing systems.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-cyan-400">Any Technology Stack</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-100">
                Language and framework agnostic. Bounded contexts are a thinking pattern, not a technology constraint.
                Use whatever tools work best for each context.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <section class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-600 to-orange-600 rounded-lg p-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Experience the Breakthrough?</h2>
            <p class="text-lg mb-6 opacity-90">
              See the proof in real production systems and learn how to apply this to your projects.
            </p>
            <div class="space-x-4">
              <a href="/proof" class="inline-block bg-white text-gray-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                See the Proof
              </a>
              <a href="/platform" class="inline-block border-2 border-white text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-gray-900 transition-colors">
                Explore the Platform
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>